{
  "texts": [
    "There also seems to be more discussion in The Guardian of the impact on the economy of the pandemic.",
    "The Guardian and the Mail also pick up the theme of the food industry.",
    "This does not seem to be as prominent in the Mirror and The Times, so is not picked up as a separate topic.",
    "As we had anticipated, climate change is another strand of the public debate.",
    "It seems to be covered with more intensity in The Guardian, where it is a separate topic, but all newspapers pay attention to the related topics of renewable and green energy."
  ]
}